# Entity & relationship rules

## Platform vs Tenant

- Platform: `m:model X Platform` → `App\Models\Platform\X`, migration `platform/`
- Tenant: `m:model X Tenant` → `App\Models\Tenant\X`, migration `tenant/`
- Mỗi `create_*` migration: `$table->softDeletes()`

## Pivot M-N — NO MODEL

Bảng chỉ map 2 entity → **migration only**:

- Không `php artisan m:model PostTag`
- Không Controller/Action cho pivot
- Khai báo `belongsToMany` trên **cả 2 model cha**
- CRUD pivot: `$parent->children()->sync()` trong **parent Action**

Ví dụ generic: `post_tag`, `role_user`, `product_category`

## Child hasMany/hasOne

- **Có model** + migration
- Relationship trên aggregate cha (`Order`, `Article`)
- Sync trong **cha Action** — không Service cho từng child row đơn giản

## Relationship vs Service

| Tình huống | Dùng |
|------------|------|
| belongsToMany / hasMany / hasOne / belongsTo | Parent **Action** + `BaseAction::syncRelations` |
| Eager load nested | Parent **Query** `includes()` |
| 2 model không liên quan Eloquent | **Service** (`Modules/*/Services/`) |
| Webhook, import, OAuth | **Service** |

```php
// ✅ Related — Action
$post->tags()->sync($tagIds);

// ❌ Pivot model class
class PostTag extends Model {}

// ✅ Unrelated — Service
class CsvImportService { ... }
```
